definition: Qianjiang sub-prefecture level city in Hubei
Qianjiang sub-prefecture level city in Hubei

sentences.english: The sedimentary environment of Qianjiang Formation is a reducing environment.
sentences.chinese: 潛江組沉積環境是一種還原環境。

sentences.english: Qianjiang City endeavored to improve the employment environment for rural workers in cities.
sentences.chinese: 潛江市着力改善農民進城就業環境。

sentences.english: The roadbed of a 300-metre section rail in Qianjiang city collapsed on Friday.
sentences.chinese: 星期五，潛江市300米長的鐵路路基塌陷。

sentences.english: Non-sandstone reservoirs within salt-layers of self-generation and self-storage exist in Qianjiang Formation.
sentences.chinese: 在江漢盆地潛江凹陷潛江組發育鹽間非砂岩油氣藏。
